'''Iẓi'''<ref>https://amawal.net/i%E1%BA%93i</ref> (s tfinaɣ : ⵉⵥⵉ, s Tasrɣint : المرارة, s Tfṛansist : Vésicule biliaire) iga yan usknaf imẓẓin, ixwan sg ugnsu. Ar gis ittmunu yan uḥruray<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref> igan awraɣ ([[Aḥruray awraɣ]]) urta iddi s ilawin (nɣ ilawan nɣ iẓṛman) imẓẓayn n ufgan<ref>https://ar.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A9</ref>.

illa iẓi g izddar n [[Tasa]], ard ittacka uḥruray awraɣ sg tasa s iẓin, ar gis ittmunu ilma iddu s ilawin imẓẓayn bac ad yaws g ubṭṭu n tafrdeddist<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref>.

